          "It took the man until 1 am to get the Bentley started and out of the garage. The limo service owner believes the person wasn’t familiar with how to drive such a vehicle, which isn’t like most modern cars. Also, the Bentley has been modified with an American transmission and antilock brakes. It also has a new engine instead of the original powerplant."
